   - Google Search Console: "Sitemaps" section
   - Bing Webmaster Tools: Submit via dashboard
   - robots.txt: Add "Sitemap: https://your-domain.com/sitemap.xml"
   - Ping (optional): http://www.google.com/ping?sitemap=[sitemap-url]

5. What to Include:
   ✅ All public pages you want indexed
   ✅ Recent content (higher priority)
   ✅ Updated lastmod dates (accurate)
   ✅ Canonical URLs only

6. What to Exclude:
   ❌ Duplicate content
   ❌ Pages blocked by robots.txt
   ❌ Pages with noindex meta tag
   ❌ Admin/private pages
   ❌ Paginated pages (only include first page or canonical)

7. Image Sitemaps:
   - Include images for better image search ranking
   - Max 1,000 images per URL entry
   - Use image:loc for image URL
   - Add title and caption for context

