   - Use video:video element for video content
   - Include video:title, video:description
   - Specify video:thumbnail_loc
   - Add video:duration

9. For AI Crawlers:
   - Recent content (lastmod) is prioritized by LLMs
   - High priority pages get more attention
   - Combine with llms.txt for best results

